ieste-teatro-verdimacbeth/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Trieste, Teatro Verdi:&#8221;Macbeth&#8221;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/03/priscilla-baglioninuovo-direttore-artistico-del-teatro-della-fortuna-di-fano/" rel="next">Priscilla Baglioni:nuovo direttore artistico del Teatro della Fortuna di Fano <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><h2 class="comments-title"> 3 comments</h2><ol class="commentlist"><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-16670"> <article id="comment-16670" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/d164cf1ca04d2e441ec70e5ad773bb03?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">luigi</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/03/roma-teatro-delloperai-due-foscari/#comment-16670"><time datetime="2013-03-14T20:04:51+00:00">14 marzo 2013 at 20:04</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>critica completa, esauriente, competente, molto ben fatta</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li><li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-16672"> <article id="comment-16672" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/0094ea22cc655d16928950011d873a23?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn"><a h